---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<section id="about" class="min-h-screen bg-white py-20 px-8" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h2 id="about-heading" class="text-5xl font-bold mb-16 opacity-0 transform translate-y-10 transition-all duration-700 ease-out slide-up">
        About Me
      </h2>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-3xl p-12 shadow-lg opacity-0 transform translate-y-10 transition-all duration-700 ease-out delay-200 slide-up">
        <p class="font-normal text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
          I'm a technology enthusiast with a passion for crafting digital experiences that make a difference. My journey in tech is driven by the belief that well-designed solutions can transform how people interact with technology.
        </p>
        
        <p class="font-normal text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
          What sets me apart is my meticulous attention to detail, particularly in creating finely-tuned development environments. I believe that a well-crafted workspace is the foundation for building exceptional products. This mindset extends to every project I undertake – from code architecture to user interface design.
        </p>

        <p class="font-normal text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
          Over the past year, I've developed a deep appreciation for design principles and their impact on user experience. This journey has transformed how I approach projects, bringing a harmonious blend of functionality and aesthetics to everything I create.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8">
          <h3 class="text-center text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Core Focus Areas</h3>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <li class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <span class="font-medium text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Digital Solutions</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-2">Building technology that solves real-world challenges</p>
            </li>
            <li class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <span class="font-medium text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Development Environment</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-2">Crafting efficient, optimized workspaces</p>
            </li>
            <li class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <span class="font-medium text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Design Integration</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-2">Merging functionality with aesthetic appeal</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        
        <nav aria-label="Social media links" class="mt-6">
          <ul class="flex gap-8 items-center list-none p-0">
            <li>
              <a 
                href="https://github.com/Kameleon21" 
                class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors" 
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                aria-label="Visit my GitHub profile"
              >
                <Icon name="mdi:github" class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out" aria-hidden="true"/>
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a 
                href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kamil-rogozinski/" 
                class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors" 
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                aria-label="Connect with me on LinkedIn"
              >
                <Icon name="mdi:linkedin" class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out" aria-hidden="true"/>
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a 
                href="https://www.tiktok.com/@kamil_rogozinski" 
                class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors" 
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                aria-label="Follow me on Instagram"
              >
                <Icon name="ic:outline-tiktok" class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out" aria-hidden="true"/>
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a 
                href="mailto:kamilrogozinski29@gmail.com" 
                class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors"
                aria-label="Send me an email"
              >
